Package de.fraunhofer.iais.eis

Interface Connector

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Described, InfrastructureComponent, ManagedEntity, ModelClass
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AppStore, BaseConnector, Broker, ParIS, TrustedConnector
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AppStoreImpl, BaseConnectorImpl, BrokerImpl, ParISImpl, TrustedConnectorImpl
    public interface Connector
extends InfrastructureComponent
    Dedicated communication server for sending and receiving data in compliance with the Connector specification. There are different types of Connectors according to provided capabilities.
